This study will be an observational study in which patients who have been prescribed Metanx(R) are invited to participate in surveys regarding their experiences with Metanx(R).

 The purpose of this study is to increase the understanding of the role of Metanx(R) in managing diabetic neuropathy, provide patients with personalized education and support, and contribute to the overall understanding of the needs and concerns of patients being treated for diabetic neuropathy.

